{"tid":350044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭落藥塞入篋禁錮7日  英國20歲女模被攝影師當性奴拍賣","createTime":"2017-08-07T03:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T06:47:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4f490177317c3b56d1c88aa3942a0b7a48f0d1","tid":350044,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170807/large/ig01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170807%2Flarge%2Fig01.jpg&h=e1eefe5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國一名20歲模特兒疑被誘騙至意大利米蘭後，遭人下藥綁架塞入行李箱，送到一處農莊禁錮7日，被拍下裸照放到暗網當作性奴拍賣，底價達23萬英鎊（234.5萬港元），但綁匪得悉她已為人母後將她釋放。意大利警方拘捕一名波蘭男子。<br />\n<br />\n意大利警方前日公佈案件，指該名模特兒上月10日應邀飛抵米蘭參與攝影工作，惟翌日進入說好的拍攝地點時，遭到兩名男子襲擊和注射麻醉科藥物氯胺酮，拍下裸照，並將她塞入行李箱放到車尾箱，送至逾190里外、都靈附近的一處農莊禁錮，其間鎖上手銬和困在木箱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170807/large/a1301b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170807%2Flarge%2Fa1301b.gif&h=f06513a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■受害人一直被手銬鎖住。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170807/large/a1301c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170807%2Flarge%2Fa1301c.gif&h=3ccf1337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員示範受害人如何被綑綁和塞入行李箱。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">指明可安排「送貨」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n綁匪其間將受害人的裸照放上暗網，把她當作「商品」拍賣，照片中她露出左乳躺在地上、僅穿着絨質性感服飾，腹上放有一張聯絡卡片，旁邊有文字列明她的歲數、身材、種族和被擄地點等，形容她非常「純潔」，又指明可安排「送貨」，但國際販運另計。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，綁匪後來得悉受害人已為一孩之母後，改而以23萬英鎊勒索其經理人公司，但後來將贖金降至5萬英鎊（51萬港元），並威脅一旦報警便殺死受害人。綁匪最終在7月17日將受害人載至米蘭的英國大使館，翌日被警方拘捕，已承認綁架指控。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">獲綁匪釋放　黨規不准綁架人母</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170807/large/a1301a.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170807%2Flarge%2Fa1301a.gif&d=%2BbNNOIDYeHgad%2F0WfzAweJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c2c7e99d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170807%2Flarge%2Fa1301a.gif&h=b06974b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170807/large/a1301a.gif</a><br />\n■疑犯赫巴<br />\n<br />\n警方指，現年30歲疑犯赫巴，是居於英國伯明翰的波蘭籍移民，相信無人曾交付任何贖金，正調查是否有同黨，以及動機為贖金，抑或純粹騙人出錢「買人」。傳媒相信他是犯罪組織「黑死病集團」（Black Death group）的頭目，其「黨規列明不准綁架人母」。<br />\n<br />\n警方未有公開受害人身份，但有英國傳媒指受害人是前第三頁女郎艾林（Chloe Ayling）。《星期日鏡報》指她只記得在失去意識前，行李箱從上笠落的一刻。其友人受訪表示：「他們（家人）以為不會再見到她回來，她到地獄走了一遭，我們只想帶她回家。」米蘭警員費拉里指受害人承受極大心理壓力，非常恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/英國《星期日鏡報》"},{"pid":"097930c90bbc036e949e843da3858b311f3459d7","tid":350044,"uid":99364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"078e749df9db703d4c4b889bc5dd04505a629678","tid":350044,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:27:23.000Z","msg":"好有道義嘅黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87139236a6bcc7f7840db60db46a5498be1223b","tid":350044,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669bd9a08eafc88ede9c1c6a65a61f504a38d13f","tid":350044,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:29:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好有道義嘅黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class